                "shortName": "6B3TM-01U",
                "description": "An upgraded 6B3TM-01 armored rig in khaki. Originally developed as modified Soviet general army body armor and used during the war in Afghanistan, the 6B3TM-01 combines protective armor with integrated magazine and grenade pouches. This reinforced variant has been fitted with improved protective inserts and repaired carrier sections, increasing its protection to Class 5 at the cost of additional weight and reduced comfort."
